basic functionalities:

add transactions and tag them. have them be deducted from the total budget for the week. whatever is left over is savings for future weeks

funcontest between friends. i saved x% of my total budget to friends

stats graph that tracks all ur previous expenses and groups them into categories so you know where your money is going



Form:

-Name of transaction
-Price of transaction
-List of categories

Confirm button - inserts data into database, navigate back to the homescreen